data.description: Welcome to your dream home! Nestled in a serene neighborhood, this exquisite 5-bedroom, 3-bathroom residence offers the perfect blend of luxury and comfort. As you step through the front door, you're greeted by a bright and airy entryway that sets the tone for the entire home. The spacious floor plan seamlessly connects the various living spaces, creating an inviting atmosphere. At the heart of the home is the gourmet kitchen, featuring granite countertops, stainless steel appliances with a gas range oven, a large kitchen island, and a convenient kitchen pantry. The kitchen effortlessly flows into the living and dining room areas, providing an ideal setting for gatherings and socializing. The main level hosts the luxurious master suite, complete with a 5-piece master bathroom and a large walk-in closet. Pamper yourself in the soothing deep soaking tub or rejuvenate in the separate stand-up shower. Two additional well-appointed bedrooms, a second full-size bathroom, and a main level laundry room complete the main level. Venture downstairs to discover a grand recreation room that offers endless possibilities—whether you envision a movie room, a playroom, a home gym space, or both, this space can adapt to your lifestyle. Two more spacious bedrooms and another full bathroom provide additional comfort and functionality on the lower level. Step outside to the large fenced-in backyard, meticulously xeriscaped landscaping offers both beauty and functionality. The oversized patio includes a gazebo that beckons you to enjoy outdoor gatherings with guests. Enjoy the golf course, local walking trails, a clubhouse, gym, pools, local parks, and local D-49 district schools within walking distance. This home and community are not just a residence but a lifestyle. Don't miss the opportunity to make this magnificent house your home. Schedule a showing today.
